Double-difference adjoint seismic tomography
Yanhua O. Yuan; Frederik J. Simons; Jeroen Tromp
Geophys. J. Int. 2016 : ggw233v1-ggw233.
http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/gji/ggw233

To run the numerical experiments in the paper
>> cd $seisDD/GJI2016

Exp1 -- figure 1-3
>> cd Exp1
>> ./run_this_example.sh
>> cd submit_job
To visualize 
>> python $seisDD/auxiliaries/visualize/plot_bin  ./RESULTS/kernel/Scale0_CC_DD/misfit_kernel/ beta_kernel_smooth 4

Exp2 -- figure 4-10
>> cd Exp2
>> ./run_this_example.sh
>> cd submit_job
Experiment IIA -- by default
./submit.sh 
Experiment IIB -- change ``time_function_type=1'' in DATA/SOURCE 
./submit.sh
Experiment IIC -- change ``tshift=-1.0'' in SU_process/process_obs.sh
./submit.sh

Exp3 -- figure 11-12
>> cd Exp3
>> ./run_this_example.sh
>> cd submit_job

Exp4 -- figure 13
>> cd Exp4
>> ./run_this_example.sh
>> cd submit_job

Exp5 -- figure 14 
>> cd Exp5
>> ./run_this_example.sh
>> cd submit_job
